{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"6e7fe8fb-9ab3-43f2-aa22-3378c5a71358","content":"The template looks mostly well-structured but has a few issues before publishing:\n\n**Missing required field:**\n- `$schema` — recommended for validation: `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"`\n\n**Missing recommended fields:**\n- `preferNameDirectory: true` — standard for project templates\n- `groupIdentity` — needed if you plan multiple related templates\n- `precedence` — useful for template versioning/overrides\n\n**Potential concerns:**\n- `\"identity\"` uses a placeholder company name (`MyCompany`) — make sure this matches your actual NuGet package ID namespace.\n- No `\"description\"` field — NuGet gallery and `dotnet new list` will show a blank description.\n\n**Verdict:** Not quite ready. At minimum, add a `description` and the `$schema` reference, and replace placeholder names with real values before publishing.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"19e5c714-b27f-48b5-b337-1b7f66d72451","outputTokens":202,"requestId":"5016:26F840:136BE2E:15D98D8:6A0670B5"},"id":"85f55a30-0378-41ab-8dad-533aa1db0bd9","timestamp":"2026-05-15T01:02:53.138Z","parentId":"42ed8703-bcce-41f2-97ea-7d705292eb2e"}
